<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Privacy Policy — NameAtlas: Baby Names</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --brand-1: #7a5cfa;
    --brand-2: #ff6fae;
    --ink: #1c1c1e;
    --muted: #6b6b70;
    --bg: #ffffff;
    --card: #faf8ff;
    --border: #ece8f6;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: var(--bg);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-1), var(--brand-2));
    color: #fff;
    padding: 56px 24px 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .hero h1 { margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 28px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .hero p { margin: 0; opacity: 0.92; font-size: 15px; }
  main {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: -24px auto 64px;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }
  .card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 28px 26px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(122, 92, 250, 0.08);
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin: 28px 0 8px;
    color: var(--brand-1);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  h2:first-of-type { margin-top: 4px; }
  p, li { font-size: 15.5px; color: var(--ink); }
  .muted { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13.5px; }
  a { color: var(--brand-1); }
  ul { padding-left: 22px; }
  li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .pill {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(122, 92, 250, 0.12);
    color: var(--brand-1);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  footer {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 13px;
    padding: 0 20px 48px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="hero">
    <h1>NameAtlas: Baby Names</h1>
    <p>Privacy Policy</p>
  </div>

  <main>
    <div class="card">
      <span class="pill">Last updated: June 7, 2026</span>

      <p>NameAtlas is designed to be private. This policy explains what the app does and does not do
      with your information.</p>

      <h2>We don't collect your data</h2>
      <p>NameAtlas has <strong>no account or sign-up</strong>, includes <strong>no analytics or
      advertising SDKs</strong>, and does <strong>not track you</strong> across apps or websites.
      We do not build a profile of you.</p>

      <h2>What stays on your device</h2>
      <p>Your <strong>search history</strong>, <strong>favorite names</strong>, <strong>full-name
      shortlist</strong>, and <strong>preferences</strong> (such as a surname for full-name previews)
      are stored <strong>only on your device</strong>. We never receive them, and they are removed if
      you delete the app.</p>

      <h2>Translation requests</h2>
      <p>To translate a meaning into other languages, the word you enter is sent over a secure
      connection to the <strong>Google Cloud Translation API</strong> for processing, and the result
      is returned to the app. We do not store these requests, and they are not linked to your
      identity. Google's handling of that request is governed by Google's privacy terms:
      <a href="https://cloud.google.com/terms/cloud-privacy-notice">cloud.google.com/terms/cloud-privacy-notice</a>.</p>

      <h2>Diagnostics you choose to send</h2>
      <p>If you use <strong>Contact Developer</strong>, the app prepares an email that may include a
      basic diagnostics log (app version, device OS, and recent in-app events — no personal content).
      This is sent <strong>only when you choose to send it</strong>, to the address shown before you
      send.</p>

      <h2>Children</h2>
      <p>NameAtlas is rated 4+ and does not knowingly collect personal information from anyone,
      including children.</p>

      <h2>Changes</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy; the "Last updated" date above will reflect any changes.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this policy? Email
      <a href="mailto:pixieface92@gmail.com">pixieface92@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    © 2026 NameAtlas
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
